            <section id="java">
                <h1>Anglr Syntax Rules for Java Programming Language</h1>
                <hr />
                <h4>Introduction</h4>
                <p>
                    This pragraph introduces Anglr syntax rules for Java programming language (early working copy). They are copied from <a href="https://docs.oracle.com/javase/specs/jls/se17/html/index.html">this website</a>
                    and customized for Anglr.
                </p>
                <hr />
